    "IdSpeaker": "NPC101",
    "cnSpeaker": "Zack",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "\"Webb 先生刚出事，你管账的，酒吧有什么生意你比谁都清楚。我想问几个问题。\"",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
