    "IdSpeaker": "NPC105",
    "cnSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "enSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "\"私人的。\"他重复了一遍，这次语气更平，像是决定了的。\n他退回到自己椅子旁边站着，没有坐下，只是看着 Zack。\n\"Brennan 先生，我能回答的都回答了。您有别的事情要问吗？\"",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
    "next": "205104035",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
    "ParameterInt1": 0,
    "ParameterInt2": 0,
    "videoEpisode": "EPI01",
