    "cnSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "enSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "Tommy 沉默了几秒。\n\"没有。\"\n就两个字，但他说这两个字时，眼神落在桌角的全家福上，停了一秒，然后移开。",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
    "next": "205104039",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
