  {
    "id": 205104043,
    "step": 40,
    "speakType": 2,
    "waitTime": 0,
    "IdSpeaker": "NPC105",
    "cnSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "enSpeaker": "Tommy",
    "Location": "",
    "cnAction": "",
    "cnWords": "\"Brennan 先生，今晚是舞会，人很杂。\"他的语气恢复了那种受控的合作感，\"我没有盯着来往的人，我在这里处理账目。\"\n他顿了顿。\n\"Morrison 探长和他的人是正式来的，我见到了。其他的...我说不清楚。\"",
    "enAction": "",
    "enWords": "",
    "next": "205104044",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
    "ParameterInt0": 0,
